# SVN Info: $Id$

#####################################################################
##                           TAPSMaintain                          ##
##                                                                 ##
##               Universal TAPS maintenance software               ##
##                                                                 ##
##                            Changelog                            ##
##                                                                 ##
#####################################################################


0.3.0 : 
* removed support for old slowcontrol system via libtcpip

0.2.2 : Nov 11 2011
* support for veto QAC pedestal database setting

0.2.1 : Feb 14 2011
* improved fitting in TDC gain calibration module

0.2.0 : Feb 4 2011
* added TDC gain calibration module

0.1.7 : Dec 16 2010
* code refactoring

0.1.6 : Nov 24 2010
* fixed axis range issue in the check spectra module

0.1.5 : Nov 5 2010
* support for QAC pedestal database setting
* support for hexadecimal value input

0.1.4 : Aug 5 2010
* show block/ring numbers during cosmics calibration
* skip BaF2 modules of ring 1 and 2 in gain match procedure

0.1.3 : Feb 24 2010
* Support for the new taps00 server
* Various small improvements and bugfixes

0.1.2 : Feb 18 2008
* Support for 72 PbWO4 elements
* Fixed some fitting problems with ROOT 5.22
* Added PbWO4 veto detectors to the spectra checking module
* small bugfixes

0.1.1 : Nov 14 2008
* Peak can be corrected manually in cosmics calibration module
* HV values are now written channel per channel to the HVServer
* Protection against bad value setting in TAPS database module
* Removed possibility to perform LED calibration without energy
  calibration (possibly dangerous)
* Improved fitting in cosmics calibration for PbWO4 detectors
* Set PbWO4 mips energy loss to 29.5 MeV
* various bugfixes

0.1.0 : Jul 2 2008
* Initial release

